data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled on a generous .2 acre corner lot, offering both space and privacy in a quiet neighborhood. Built in 2000, this cozy retreat features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms spread across 959 square feet, with a small covered porch in the front, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or greeting guests. With a 2-car garage, this home provides comfort and convenience. Its ideal location offers easy access to amenities and the beautiful nampa greenbelt while the spacious lot presents potential for personalization and expansion. Don't miss the chance to make this delightful abode your own – schedule a showing today!
